  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0b89\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0b95\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8 - \u0b8e\u0bae\u0bcd.\u0b8f.\u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba9\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Court order has nothing to do with removal of demonstrators - MA Sumanthran",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Tamil National Federation Media Spokesperson and Member of Parliament MA Sumanthran said that the removal of the Presidential Secretariat demonstrators has nothing to do with the court order.",
        "This was stated by MA Sumanthran at a media conference held at the Sri Lankan Tamil Republic Party's Vadamarachi office.",
        "JR 39 years after the July riots of 1983 during Jayawardena's presidency, J.R. Yesterday, when Ranil Wickremesinghe, Jayawardene's cousin, was the President, there was an attack on Khalimugat.",
        "The court order is that one should not go within 50 meters around the Bandaranaike statue by mentioning his name. The court order was unrelated to the removal of the Presidential Secretariat protesters.",
        "The attack was carried out by government forces in the dark after protesters said they would retake the presidential secretariat. The international community condemned the attack. The representative of the main country directly told the president that if such an incident happens again, we will help you.",
        "Last May 9 attack was carried out by gangsters. Yesterday's attack was carried out by government forces. Why did Ranil Wickramasinghe who condemned the May 9 attack not condemn it?",
        "Within hours the executive replaced Ranil. Yesterday's attack left the country reeling."
      ],
